</p>
<p><span class="headers">July 12, 2003 - Gibber times 10!!</span>
<p>
It seems I was premature in promising that the next update would be from the new site. There was just a loud BANG from downstairs ... the House Ogre's computer literally blew up ... it'll be a few days before the replacement power supply is here. <i>(And we mean literally blew up!! I almost fell out of my chair in startlement. - Ngreth)</i> You guessed it ... there's irreplaceable info on that machine that we need in order to move the DB from the test site to the production side. We'll give a new ETA when able.</p>
<p>
